lead_paragraph: Belgium have made three changes for their Euro 2016 quarter-final against Wales on Friday with manager Mark Wilmots forced to cover for an injury and a suspension among his defenders.

headline.print_headline: Belgium Make Three Changes, Wales One for Quarter-Final
